OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782901111
OL,3,CForest Green Rovers scrap women's team
OL,4,Cfor 26/27 season
OL,6,FForest Green Rovers have announced
OL,7,Fthey've scrapped their women's team
OL,8,Ffor the 2026-27 season, to concentrate
OL,9,Fresources on returning their men's
OL,10,Fside to the English Football League.
OL,12,FThe club say they will also end their
OL,13,Fpartnership with Hartpury's Elite
OL,14,FTraining Centre for Girls.
OL,16,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said
OL,17,Fthis "isn't goodbye to women's
OL,18,Ffootball" at the club.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
