FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782901111
OL,3,CForest Green Rovers scrap women's team
OL,4,Cfor 26/27 season
OL,6,FThey added: "We had been in
OL,7,Fdiscussions with Hartpury Uni about a
OL,8,Fpartnership, but the Uni made a
OL,9,Fdecision that ruled out the
OL,10,Fpossibility of a joint team.
OL,12,F"This means we'll also be stepping
OL,13,Fback from our joint involvement with
OL,14,FHartpury's Elite Training Centre for
OL,15,Fgirls aged 9 to 16.
OL,17,F"Our partnership with Hartpury has
OL,18,Fbeen worthwhile and valued, we'll
OL,19,Fcontinue to support them as they
OL,20,Fexplore ways to take the programme
OL,21,Fforward through Hartpury Women FC.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782901111
OL,3,CForest Green Rovers scrap women's team
OL,4,Cfor 26/27 season
OL,6,F"Forest Green Rovers is committed to
OL,7,Freturning to the EFL as quickly as
OL,8,Fpossible, and that means concentrating
OL,9,Four resources and efforts on
OL,10,Fstrengthening the Club and achieving
OL,11,Fthat goal.
OL,13,F"This isn't goodbye to women's
OL,14,Ffootball at Forest Green.
OL,16,F"We'd like to return to it in the
OL,17,Ffuture, when the time is right and
OL,18,Fwhen we can build a programme that is
OL,19,Fsustainable and successful for the
OL,20,Flong term.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
