PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782901111
OL,3,CForest Green Rovers scrap women's team
OL,4,Cfor 26/27 season
OL,6,F"We'd like to thank the players,
OL,7,Fstaff, volunteers and supporters who
OL,8,Fhave been part of the women's
OL,9,Fprogramme and wish them every success
OL,10,Ffor the future."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
